## GRADIENTS OF CHAOS

### The Brainrot Fade
```
linear-gradient(135deg, #FF00FF 0%, #00FF00 50%, #FFD700 100%)
CSS: background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF00FF 0%, #00FF00 50%, #FFD700 100%);
Usage: Maximum visual damage
```

### The Shadow Ban
```
linear-gradient(180deg, #0A0A0A 0%, #808080 100%)
CSS: background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0A0A0A 0%, #808080 100%);
Usage: When you've been banned too long
```

### The 3AM Special
```
linear-gradient(45deg, #4B0082 0%, #0A0A0A 50%, #FF00FF 100%)
CSS: background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4B0082 0%, #0A0A0A 50%, #FF00FF 100%);
Usage: Witching hour thumbnails
```

### The Algorithm's Tears
```
linear-gradient(90deg, #00FFFF 0%, #808080 100%)
CSS: background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00FFFF 0%, #808080 100%);
Usage: When the algorithm gives up
```

