## COLOR COMBINATIONS TO AVOID

❌ **The Normie Neutral**
   - Any beige, any gray, any "professional" color
   - Result: Zero brainrot, maximum mid energy

❌ **The Corporate Safe**
   - Navy blue, forest green, burgundy
   - Result: LinkedIn energy (death)

❌ **The Pastel Disaster**
   - Any pastel anything
   - Result: Soft girl aesthetic (the algorithm pities you)

